sequenceDiagram
    actor U as User
    participant Medium as Medium-Domain
    participant MetaW as Metadata-Worker
    participant MediumW as Medium-Worker
    participant User as User-Domain
    participant Task as Task-Domain
    participant Exif as Exiftool
    participant D as Database
    participant T as Temp Storage
    participant S as Permanent Storage
    participant E as EventBus

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# UPLOAD PHASE (synchronous - user waits)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
    U ->> +Medium: Upload image
    Medium ->> +User: Reserve Quota
    User ->> D: Update User Quota
    User ->> -E: QuotaReservedEvent
    par
        Medium ->> T: Store image temporarily
    and
        Medium ->> D: Create Medium
        Medium ->> D: Create Medium Item
    end
    Medium ->> E: MediumCreatedEvent
    Medium ->> E: MediumItemCreatedEvent
    Medium ->> +User: Commit Quota
    User ->> -E: QuotaCommittedEvent
    Medium -->> -U: MediumId

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# TASK CREATION (Task domain listens for trigger events)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
    E -->> Task: Handle MediumCreatedEvent
    Task ->> D: Create metadata_extraction task (pending)

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# METADATA EXTRACTION (Metadata Worker handles backpressure)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
    E ->> MetaW: Handle MediumCreatedEvent
    Note over MetaW: Adds to internal queue<br/>(bounded, returns immediately)

    Note over MetaW: Worker loop with semaphore
    MetaW ->> E: MetadataExtractionStartedEvent
    E -->> Task: Handle MetadataExtractionStartedEvent
    Task ->> D: Update task (running)

    MetaW ->> +Exif: Extract Metadata
    Exif -->> -MetaW: Raw Metadata

    alt Extraction Success
        MetaW ->> D: Save Metadata
        MetaW ->> E: MetadataExtractedEvent

        E -->> Task: Handle MetadataExtractedEvent
        Task ->> D: Complete metadata_extraction task
        Task ->> D: Create move_to_storage task (pending)

    else Extraction Failure
        MetaW ->> E: MetadataExtractionFailedEvent

        E -->> Task: Handle MetadataExtractionFailedEvent
        Task ->> D: Fail metadata_extraction task (+ error)

        Note over User: Could release quota on<br/>terminal failure (not shown)
    end

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# MOVE TO STORAGE (Medium Worker handles backpressure)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
    E ->> MediumW: Handle MetadataExtractedEvent
    Note over MediumW: Adds to internal queue<br/>(bounded, returns immediately)

    Note over MediumW: Worker loop with semaphore
    MediumW ->> E: MoveToStorageStartedEvent
    E -->> Task: Handle MoveToStorageStartedEvent
    Task ->> D: Update task (running)

    MediumW ->> D: Get Medium
    MediumW ->> MediumW: Update entity with metadata fields

    alt Move Success
        MediumW ->> T: Read from temp
        MediumW ->> S: Write to permanent
        MediumW ->> T: Delete from temp
        MediumW ->> D: Save Medium (new path)
        MediumW ->> E: MediumMovedToStorageEvent

        E -->> Task: Handle MediumMovedToStorageEvent
        Task ->> D: Complete move_to_storage task

    else Move Failure
        MediumW ->> E: MoveToStorageFailedEvent

        E -->> Task: Handle MoveToStorageFailedEvent
        Task ->> D: Fail move_to_storage task (+ error)

        Note over User: Could release quota on<br/>terminal failure (not shown)
    end

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# EVENT -> TASK MAPPING SUMMARY
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# MediumCreatedEvent            -> Create metadata_extraction (pending)
# MetadataExtractionStartedEvent -> Update metadata_extraction (running)
# MetadataExtractedEvent        -> Complete metadata_extraction
#                               -> Create move_to_storage (pending)
# MetadataExtractionFailedEvent -> Fail metadata_extraction
# MoveToStorageStartedEvent     -> Update move_to_storage (running)
# MediumMovedToStorageEvent     -> Complete move_to_storage
# MoveToStorageFailedEvent      -> Fail move_to_storage
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════